    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey 👋 ,\r\nI'm reusing the work done on this branch so we can release it with another dataset (we're going with Algolia's blog data). \r\n\r\nPreview → https://deploy-preview-3915--instantsearchjs.netlify.app/examples/media/\r\n\r\nThere are differences between the two datasets that require some changes:\r\n\r\n| Old dataset | New dataset | Notes |\r\n| ----------- | ------------- | ------ |\r\n| categories | coauthors |  |\r\n| topics | categories |  |\r\n| locations | N/A |  |\r\n| date | N/A | Can be added back later if the dataset is updated with this attribute |\r\n| sortBy | N/A |  |\r\n\r\nI also edited the wording and added more info regarding the authors (avatar and job title).\r\n\r\nStill needs to be done:\r\n\r\n- [x] remove unused components from codebase\r\n- [x] update dependencies\r\n\r\nLet me know if I missed something.",
